snippet.title: Wealth Project Trailer - Release coming on 27th!
snippet.description:
Wealth Project is a new inspiring educational game about Wealth building knowledge that is released on the Steam platform on 27.09.2024 for Windows. 

Find us also in STEAM store and make sure to add to your Wishlist!
